Number Pattern 2
Send Feedback
Print the following pattern
Pattern for N = 4


The dots represent spaces.



Input Format :
N (Total no. of rows)
Output Format :
Pattern in N lines
Sample Input :
5
Sample Output :


The dots represent spaces.


#include <iostream>
using namespace std;
int main() {
    int n;
    cin >> n;
    int i = 1;
    while (i <= n) {
        int j = 1;
        int val = i - 1;
        int k = 1;
        while (k <= n - i) {
            cout << " ";
            k = k + 1;
        }
        while (j <= i) {
            j = j + 1;
            val = val + 1;
            cout << val;
        }
        i = i + 1;
        cout << endl;
    }
}
